title: Deaths of British tourists abroad 2009 to 2014
summary: Overall Number of deaths has increased over the Year.
Number of deaths is roughly constant from 2009/2010 to 2010/2011, and lastly slightly increasing from 2010/2011 to 2011/2012.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2010/2011 and 2011/2012.
Maximum Number of deaths, about 6237.0 was reported at Year 2011/2012
Minimum Number of deaths about 5930.0 was reached at Year 2009/2010
